{"id":549321,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/01/【图说天朝】中文信息污染/","date":"2017-01-17T03:41:47Z","modified":"2017-01-17T03:41:47Z","title":"【图说天朝】中文信息污染一例","content":"<p>近日，台湾移民署新竹市服务站为了让部分印尼与马来华人感受春节氛围，亲近其原国习俗，特地准备红色、绿色红包两种。然而不少国内官媒在报道此事时曲解事实，称为“绿营动作”、“绿化伎俩”。</p>\n<p>@小粉红研究爱好者E：墙里墙外&#8230;&#8230;</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/006A48Cmgw1fbsmtceic0j30hs0vljx8.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-549323\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/006A48Cmgw1fbsmtceic0j30hs0vljx8.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"799\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/006A48Cmgw1fbsmtceic0j30hs0vljx8.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/006A48Cmgw1fbsmtceic0j30hs0vljx8-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/006A48Cmgw1fbsmtceic0j30hs0vljx8-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/006A48Cmgw1fbsmuh8fxej30hs0vln2b.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-549324\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/006A48Cmgw1fbsmuh8fxej30hs0vln2b.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"799\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/006A48Cmgw1fbsmuh8fxej30hs0vln2b.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/006A48Cmgw1fbsmuh8fxej30hs0vln2b-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/006A48Cmgw1fbsmuh8fxej30hs0vln2b-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/006A48Cmgw1fbsmvav88yj30hs0vl42r.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-549325\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/006A48Cmgw1fbsmvav88yj30hs0vl42r.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"799\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/01/006A48Cmgw1fbsmvav88yj30hs0vl42r.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017